#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/unstructured/tri.rst:22
msgid "WW3 Triangular Mesh"
msgstr "WW3 三角メッシュ"

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/unstructured/tri.rst:24
msgid ""
"This example demonstrates how to render an unstructured triangular mesh."
msgstr "この例では、非構造化三角形メッシュをレンダリングする方法を示します。"

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/unstructured/tri.rst:27
msgid "📋 Summary"
msgstr "📋 まとめ"

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/unstructured/tri.rst:29
msgid ""
"Creates a mesh from 1D latitude and longitude unstructured points and "
"connectivity."
msgstr ""

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/unstructured/tri.rst:31
msgid ""
"The resulting mesh contains triangular cells. The connectivity is required "
"to construct the cells by indexing into the unstructured points."
msgstr "連結性は、構造化されていない点にインデックスを付けてセルを構成するために必要です。"

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/unstructured/tri.rst:34
msgid ""
"WAVEWATCH III (WW3) sea surface wave significant height data is located on "
"mesh nodes/points, which are then interpolated across the mesh faces/cells."
msgstr "WAVEWATCH III (WW3) の海面波の有義波高データは、メッシュの節点/点に配置され、メッシュ面/セルに渡って補間されます。"

#: ../../geovista/docs/src/generated/gallery/unstructured/tri.rst:37
msgid ""
"Finally, a Natural Earth base layer is rendered along with Natural Earth "
"coastlines."
msgstr "最後に、Natural Earthの海岸線とともに、Natural Earthのベースレイヤーがレンダリングされます。"

